::Firearm/Rex::

Firearm raises his cannon as he sees the fire exchanged by Imprisoner and 
Brix, ready to fire at Imprisoner when Rex puts a hand on his cannon.

"Brix, stand down," he says loudly over the gunfire, "They surrendered."
